Perpetual PEP Grth        53.6    Mart Currie Int Grth        451.9
Prolific Techno           53.3    Merlin Jup Intl             435.8
B of I Wldwide           141.6    Framlington Recov           395.7
Framlington Intl          36.6    St James Pl NAm &amp; Int       370.3
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
</TEXT>
